<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٣ - <span class="c2">(١٩٦٠)</span> حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5898">مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ الْمُثَنَّى،</a> <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5509">وَابْنُ بَشَّارٍ </a>قَالَا: حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5532">مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ جَعْفَرٍ </a>، حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">شُعْبَةُ </a>بِهَذَا الْإِسْنَادِ مِثْلَهُ .<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>